<section class="event-page-hero"><h1>Dollywood Excursion</h1><p>Pigeon Forge, Tennessee</p></section>
<main class="container"><div class="event-layout"><section class="card"><img src="../images/dollywood-banner.png" alt="Dollywood Excursion Banner" class="card-image"><div class="card-body"><h2>About This Excursion</h2><p>Dollywood is a major 165-acre theme park in Pigeon Forge, Tennessee. Co-owned by country music legend Dolly Parton, it celebrates the culture and beauty of the Great Smoky Mountains. The destination combines major thrill rides with traditional Appalachian crafts, award-winning live music, and southern food.</p>
<div class="register-panel"><h2>Ready to Register?</h2><p>Complete the Google Form first, then send payment using Cash App or Apple Pay.</p><a class="button gold-button" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSew70NjYJgqdCBS-8g6Ek-wSPkg6OKiDWFWPs0jnCUrK6IFLA/viewform?usp=header" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Details & Register</a></div>
